item.description: SoftLayer_Notification_Subscriber_Delivery_Method Datatype Description Provides details for the subscriber’s delivery methods. Type: dateTime modifyDate Date the subscriber's delivery method was last modified. Type: dateTime notificationDeliveryMethodId Identifier for the notification delivery method.
